    • getWSWRLVariable

      public WSWRLVariable getWSWRLVariable(org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.IRI iri, WSWRLVariableDomain domain)
      Description copied from interface: WSWRLDataFactory
      Returns the instance of a variable that corresponds to an IRI. If no variable exists for that IRI, a new instance will be created. Otherwise it returns the instance.
